            About me
            Welcome to my personal website! I’m a senior student of Economics and Applied Math & Statistics at Macalester College, and will graduate in May 2022. I enjoy programming with R for data analytics, data visualization, and creating Shiny apps.
            
            
            Education
            Macalester College | St Paul, MN
            BA in Economics and Applied Math & Statistics, Sept. 2018 ~ Present
            
            
            Internship
            China Securities| Summer M&A Intern, July 2021 ~ August 2021
            Huatai Securities | Mutual Fund Intern, May 2021 ~ June 2021
            Prepare+Prosper | Virtual Financial Advocate, January 2021 ~ May 2021
            Macalester College | Student Fundraiser, January 2020 ~ June 2020
